    stable 2.7.2 2.6.7 2.6.6 2.6.4 2.6.3 2.6.1 2.6.0
   require gtk+

  category audio/cd audio/recorder
 attribute x11
    source ripperx/ripperX-$VERSION.tar.gz
       url "$SOURCEFORGE_URL"
  homepage http://ripperX.sourceforge.net
  estimate 400
      desc 'ripperX is a gtk+-v1.2 program to rip CD audio and encode mp3s.
It can rip and encode in parallel and has plugins for
cdparanoia, BladeEnc, Lame, GoGo, FHG (l3enc and mp3enc),
XingMp3enc, 8hz-mp3,  and the ISO encoder.
It also has support for CDDB and ID3 tags.'
